<p class="text-5 mb-8 text-charcoal-light text-weight-400">
  We make moving your website easy. Just send over a few details, and we'll take care of the rest.
</p>

<div class="mb-7">
  <h3 class="text-4 text-charcoal text-weight-550">Hosting & Server</h3>
  <ul class="text-3">
    <li><span class="text-weight-500 text-charcoal">Current host login</span> - Where your site lives now.</li>
    <li><span class="text-weight-500 text-charcoal">FTP/SFTP credentials</span> - To transfer files.</li>
    <li><span class="text-weight-500 text-charcoal">SSH access</span> - If your site runs on a server with command-line access.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="mb-7">
  <h3 class="text-4 text-charcoal text-weight-550">Database</h3>
  <ul class="text-3">
    <li><span class="text-weight-500 text-charcoal">Database login</span> - Username, password, and database name.</li>
    <li><span class="text-weight-500 text-charcoal">phpMyAdmin (or similar)</span> - To export and import data.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="mb-7">
  <h3 class="text-4 text-charcoal text-weight-550">Domain & DNS</h3>
  <ul class="text-3">
    <li><span class="text-weight-500 text-charcoal">Domain registrar login</span> - Where your domain is registered.</li>
    <li><span class="text-weight-500 text-charcoal">DNS settings</span> - To point your domain to the new site.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="mb-7">
  <h3 class="text-4 text-charcoal text-weight-550">Website Admin</h3>
  <ul class="text-3">
    <li><span class="text-weight-500 text-charcoal">CMS login</span> - WordPress, Shopify, or whatever you use.</li>
    <li><span class="text-weight-500 text-charcoal">Plugin/theme licenses</span> - If you have paid ones.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="mb-7">
  <h3 class="text-4 text-charcoal text-weight-550">Email & Services</h3>
  <ul class="text-3">
    <li><span class="text-weight-500 text-charcoal">Email provider login</span> - If emails are tied to your current host.</li>
    <li><span class="text-weight-500 text-charcoal">CDN login</span> - If you use Cloudflare or a similar service.</li>
    <li><span class="text-weight-500 text-charcoal">Analytics login</span> - Google Analytics, Search Console, etc.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div class="mb-7">
  <h3 class="text-5 text-charcoal text-weight-550">Why It Matters?</h3>
  <p>
    Not having the right credentials can delay the migration, break things, or even lose data.
  </p>
</div>
